name: Saturday 17th August (6.45pm sharp): Early Bird
description:
A 1950's Roller Derby Diner in a secret location brought to you by the people who gave you The Raven & the Writing Desk at The Milk Thistle in Bristol.

Join us for a 1950's Interactive Dining Experience in a Secret Location within Bristol City Centre on the 17th and 18th of August. 
Donn your best 1950's clobber and your dancing shoes for a night full of Cherry Cola, Chilli Dogs and 5 Dollar Shakes.

Think Grease meets Pulp Fiction on skates.

17th August 2013
6.45pm sharp
